works.complaint:
The website Jerk.com is using my photograph without  
permission and has included my name in its website which allows anyone on 

the internet to vote on whether I am a 'jerk' or not. The website also  
allows internet users to post comments about me which may be defamatory.  

This website is one of the first few hits that come up when googling my  
name and may effect future job opportunities. It is also a violation of my
 
privacy.
